			<div class="content" id="post-content-1841381">
									

<p>Added, as well as added one for <a href="/scp-208">SCP-208</a>.</p>
<p>My one regret is that there was this one thing I wrote a few months ago that I'll never be able to find. At the time, there were two humanoid SCPs on the chopping block: one was a red humanoid 682 but <em>way way better y'all</em>, the other was a&#8230;golem, I think? It was something involving being made of every mineral in the history of ever. Since they were both going down, I figured I'd write a goofy little story about an intergalactic/interdimensional arena where they both showed up to duke it out.</p>
<p>Unfortunately, in a clear case of awesome foresight, I posted it on one of the pages (I think it was on the 682 knockoff page), and it got deleted and I never saved it anywhere else. :(</p>

